.TH CYGNUS-OPEN 1.0 "March 2026" "Version 1.0" "Cygnus File Picker"
.SH NAME
cygnus-open \- minimalist file picker for Cygnus WM utilities

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B cygnus-open
[\fB\-view\fR] [\fB\-media\fR]

.SH DESCRIPTION
.B cygnus-open
is a minimalist file picker used by other Cygnus utilities like \fBcygnus-view\fR and \fBcygnus-media\fR to browse and select files. It follows the Cygnus aesthetic with thin borders and a scrollable file list.

.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-view
Filter for image files compatible with \fBcygnus-view\fR.
.TP
.B \-media
Filter for audio and video files compatible with \fBcygnus-media\fR.

.SH KEY BINDINGS
.TP
.B Up/Down Arrows
Navigate the file list.
.TP
.B Return, o
Open the selected file or directory.
.TP
.B Backspace
Go to the parent directory.
.TP
.B Escape, c
Cancel the operation and exit.

